CHAPTER 1.
Paul, an apostle of Jesus Christ by the will of God, to the saints which are at Ephesus, and to the faithful in Christ Jesus:

<w class="strong:G5485 lemma.TR:χαρις" morph="robinson:N-NSF" src="1">Grace</w> <transChange type="added">be</transChange> <w class="strong:G5213 lemma.TR:υμιν" morph="robinson:P-2DP" src="2">to you</w>, <w class="strong:G2532 lemma.TR:και" morph="robinson:CONJ" src="3">and</w> <w class="strong:G1515 lemma.TR:ειρηνη" morph="robinson:N-NSF" src="4">peace</w>, <w class="strong:G575 lemma.TR:απο" morph="robinson:PREP" src="5">from</w> <w class="strong:G2316 lemma.TR:θεου" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="6">God</w> <w class="strong:G2257 lemma.TR:ημων" morph="robinson:P-1GP" src="8">our</w> <w class="strong:G3962 lemma.TR:πατρος" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="7">Father</w>, <w class="strong:G2532 lemma.TR:και" morph="robinson:CONJ" src="9">and</w> <transChange type="added">from</transChange> <w class="strong:G2962 lemma.TR:κυριου" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="10">the Lord</w> <w class="strong:G2424 lemma.TR:ιησου" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="11">Jesus</w> <w class="strong:G5547 lemma.TR:χριστου" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="12">Christ</w>.

<w class="strong:G3588 lemma.TR:τοις" morph="robinson:T-DPN" src="19"/><w class="strong:G2128 lemma.TR:ευλογητος" morph="robinson:A-NSM" src="1">Blessed</w> <transChange type="added">be</transChange> <w class="strong:G3588 strong:G2316 lemma.TR:ο lemma.TR:θεος" morph="robinson:T-NSM robinson:N-NSM" src="2 3">the God</w> <w class="strong:G2532 lemma.TR:και" morph="robinson:CONJ" src="4">and</w> <w class="strong:G3962 lemma.TR:πατηρ" morph="robinson:N-NSM" src="5">Father</w> <w class="strong:G2257 lemma.TR:ημων" morph="robinson:P-1GP" src="8">of our</w> <w class="strong:G3588 strong:G2962 lemma.TR:του lemma.TR:κυριου" morph="robinson:T-GSM robinson:N-GSM" src="6 7">Lord</w> <w class="strong:G2424 lemma.TR:ιησου" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="9">Jesus</w> <w class="strong:G5547 lemma.TR:χριστου" morph="robinson:N-GSM" src="10">Christ</w>, <w class="strong:G3588 lemma.TR:ο" morph="robinson:T-NSM" src="11">who</w> <w class="strong:G2127 lemma.TR:ευλογησας" morph="robinson:V-AAP-NSM" src="12">hath blessed</w> <w class="strong:G2248 lemma.TR:ημας" morph="robinson:P-1AP" src="13">us</w> <w class="strong:G1722 lemma.TR:εν" morph="robinson:PREP" src="14">with</w> <w class="strong:G3956 lemma.TR:παση" morph="robinson:A-DSF" src="15">all</w> <w class="strong:G4152 lemma.TR:πνευματικη" morph="robinson:A-DSF" src="17">spiritual</w> <w class="strong:G2129 lemma.TR:ευλογια" morph="robinson:N-DSF" src="16">blessings</w> <w class="strong:G1722 lemma.TR:εν" morph="robinson:PREP" src="18">in</w> <w class="strong:G2032 lemma.TR:επουρανιοις" morph="robinson:A-DPN" src="20">heavenly</w> <transChange type="added">places</transChange> <w class="strong:G1722 lemma.TR:εν" morph="robinson:PREP" src="21">in</w> <w class="strong:G5547 lemma.TR:χριστω" morph="robinson:N-DSM" src="22">Christ</w>:
